data.description: This newly renovated property is conveniently nestled in the West Philadelphia section of Philadelphia. This 3 bed, 1 bath gem comes with newly installed Hardwood flooring throughout the first level, as well as Recessed lighting which truly complements freshly painted walls throughout. Kitchen features Stainless Steel appliances along with countertop space to spare. Second level features newly installed carpet throughout every bedroom, as well as a completely re done modernized bathroom which truly adds the finishing touch to this beauty of a home. Please don't hesitate, come take a look for yourself!!
